item.title: Nowhere Festival 2015 - Dancing Nobodies
item.description:
Nowhere Festival 2015 - Dancing Nobodies

This video is about the beauty of dancing and expressing yourself through movement. I asked these wonderful Nobodies to show their own dance. This visual memory of these beautiful people makes me so grateful! I shot this video at Nowhere Festival 2015 in the amazing desert of North Spain.

item.title: Burning Man 2013 - Burn // Ellie Goulding
item.description:
Burning Man 2013 - Burn // Ellie Goulding

In 2013, Burning Man brought 60,000 to the harsh deserts of Black Rock City near Reno for a week long experiment in art, music, self-expression and living. So what is Burning Man? Is it the world's largest bonfire? Is it a world record attempt for the most people not showering for a week?
